content.en: object-cover w-full h-full absolute inset-0 transition-opacity duration-1000

A full-featured video completely dedicated to your brand, product, or campaign.
Created in the channel's style to be organically perceived by the audience and build trust.
Development of the video idea, creative approach, and script in collaboration with the brand. Possibility to adapt the product to the blogger's content (story, challenge, experiment, etc.).
Full-scale video production in the channel's style: staging, editing, color correction, graphics, sound.
Integration throughout the entire video: logo, product, key messages, demonstration of benefits.
Publication on the main YouTube channel with a pinned link in the description and first comment. Optionally - a post in the YouTube community or stories on other social networks.
Providing statistics after 7 and 30 days: views, retention, link clicks, engagement.
For three years now, I've been living in Armenia and sharing my life here on YouTube.
In my videos, I talk about the people, culture, and inspiring stories of this amazing country - through the eyes of someone who once simply decided to stay and live here.
